name: Northern Affair
description:
Northern Affair, the pairs 3rd EP of 2009, stays true to their original thematic plan while delving into more personal subject material. “We still wanted to write about the here and now,” says Davis, “but felt like there was a back-story to every story we told on Change of Address and The Wildwood Hymns.”
          Northern Affair reaches deep both conceptually and stylistically, exploring those “back-stories” with topics from alcoholism to lost faith, wrapped in a number of different musical genres.
            “I think this process (writing 5 EPs in a year) has really shed some light on what we want our music to accomplish, both personally and professionally,” says Walker. “We started out writing about very timely experiences but the music itself has opened up doors and realizations to the point that we are now using it as a sort of cathartic therapy for past experiences.”

Track Listing:

1. Sling
2. Northern Affair
3. White Walls
4. Exclamation!
5. Steeple Chase
